Responsibilities:

Responsible for performing market research on the up-coming fashion trend;
Assemble and execute plans for seasonal brand assortment and OTB in order to meet the company’s business objective;
Products sourcing and sell-thru analysis;
Liaise with suppliers on order placing efficiency and ensure appropriate levels of stock of designated product categories are maintained;
Allocate merchandises and coordinate with shops and warehouse to smooth the stock replenishment issue;
Work closely with operations, visual merchandising team and other counterparts to maximize sales performance of responsible category;
Cultivate and maintain partnership relationship with suppliers

Requirements:

Bachelor’s degree holder
Min. 4 years’ apparel / footwear buying experience
Solid experience in branded merchandise buying, store replenishment, merchandise consolidation and product management is a must
Strong business sense with excellent negotiation, interpersonal, numerical and analytical skills
Fluent in spoken and written English, Chinese and Mandarin
Proficient in MS Excel (Pivot Table, VLookup and other formula functions)
Willing to travel
Candidate with less experience will be considered as Assistant Buyer

Interested parties please send your resume with current and expected salary by clicking "Apply Now".


